{"tid":1345162,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗黑夜】YOHO Mall聲明：有市民遇襲　職員無法聯絡警方","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:38:44.000Z","uid":99493,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"542184759ee4bb52380bf509b46b5cdb5e0a0200","tid":1345162,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:29:38.000Z","msg":"元朗周日晚上（22日）發生疑由黑社會發動的襲擊市民事件。大批身穿白衫的不明人士，晚上在元朗區多個地點，包括元朗港鐵站襲擊手無寸鐵的途人。位於西鐵元朗站的商場YOHO Mall今日（22日）發聲明，稱商場服務處職員及商場內市民發現有人遇襲後，隨即報警求助，但一直未能聯絡警方。 聲明表示，Yoho Mall服務處對於7月21日晚上有市民在港鐵元朗站通往商場的通道上遇到襲擊及受傷，深表震驚和遺憾，並向受傷市民致以慰問，希望他們早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，服務處職員及商場內市民發現有人遇襲後，隨即報警求助，但一直未能聯絡警方。最後在住宅業主陪同下，商場安排部分遇襲市民到住宅平台暫避，為他們提供水和急救用品等。商場職員其後為受傷市民作初步急救，待救護員接報到場後將受傷市民送院治理。 <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/354639/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F354639%2F&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=4c54da54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/354639/</a>"},{"pid":"801aaf185bbe6d12e12438e7ec6d4eac0928dea5","tid":1345162,"uid":99493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:30:33.000Z","msg":"以後唔敢去yoho mall"},{"pid":"1da8de7eae92b7ae56962a9210da95131df21c9b","tid":1345162,"uid":255962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"又係新地場"},{"pid":"db780e65583904c02ce116097114a06871fc8010","tid":1345162,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1da8de7eae92b7ae56962a9210da95131df21c9b","tid":1345162,"uid":255962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"又係新地場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"新地場好撚危險"},{"pid":"96ea69c65e26b942f2dddf4b12915126dd0fdb73","tid":1345162,"uid":34174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:33:35.000Z","msg":"即係平時d職員兇人就呢<br />\n欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"221460ba484809e3d5e1fd1f2bf75f83cb803f3c","tid":1345162,"uid":221696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/22/093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png&h=d969c48e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e48fa83bd223538fea934bf8da7d5f6a38c695d","tid":1345162,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:35:09.000Z","msg":"唔洗再分支線搞新地，直接用佢地幾份聲明煲大黑警設局殺死港人"},{"pid":"53a78ba8ec3b319819c3bd2141e4f2f2ee3d2ab8","tid":1345162,"uid":34577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:35:35.000Z","msg":"唔係「疑」啦，直頭係黑社會"},{"pid":"82240cafaa70df24d566be00d812be5311852f22","tid":1345162,"uid":142588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"新地場大家明啦"},{"pid":"de8a1440efd9035716dff205d56737e54d1cbc8a","tid":1345162,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"但警方聲明話同港鐵yoho有聯絡wo"}]}